---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Experience â€” Mohammed Asrar Ali" description="Work experience and measurable outcomes.">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="animate-fade-up opacity-100">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Experience</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 max-w-lg text-lg">Where I've worked and what I've shipped.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-0">
      <!-- Experience 1: TrendAI -->
      <div class="reveal relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l border-surface-200">
        <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 ring-4 ring-surface-0"></div>
        <div class="glow-card p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Software Developer Co-op</h2>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 text-xs font-mono font-medium flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="status-dot" style="width:6px;height:6px;"></span> CURRENT
              </span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">Jan 2026 &mdash; Present</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium">TrendAI &middot; Ottawa, ON</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Building and testing features for the <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">Cloud One platform</span> using Java; integrating CI/CD pipelines with Jenkins and validating deployments on AWS EC2 in an Agile team</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Ported agent support to <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">SUSE Linux 16</span>; updated deployment scripts, OS mappings, UI metadata, and versioning pages</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Delivered a report generator to a customer in just <span class="text-brand-400 font-medium">3 days</span>, helping secure an enterprise deal</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span class="tech-badge">Java</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Python</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Jenkins</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">AWS EC2</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Linux</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience 2: Maintair Aviation -->
      <div class="reveal relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l border-surface-200">
        <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 ring-4 ring-surface-0"></div>
        <div class="glow-card p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Software Engineering Intern</h2>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">May 2024 &mdash; Aug 2024</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium">Maintair Aviation &middot; Thunder Bay, ON</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Built and deployed a <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">Flask + React flight-schedule manager</span> on Azure App Service, replacing spreadsheets and reducing scheduling errors by <span class="text-brand-400 font-medium">40%</span></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Designed flight scheduling tables in Azure SQL Database and stored static assets in Blob Storage; automated weekly reporting for stakeholders</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-brand-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Implemented REST APIs secured with Managed Identities and instrumented Application Insights metrics/alerts</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span class="tech-badge">Flask</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">React</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">SQL</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Python</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience 3: Code4kids -->
      <div class="reveal relative pl-8 border-l border-surface-200">
        <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-500 ring-4 ring-surface-0"></div>
        <div class="glow-card p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Volunteer Teaching Assistant</h2>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">May 2023 &mdash; Present</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-accent-500 text-sm font-medium">Code4kids &middot; Remote, Canada</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="text-accent-500 mt-1 shrink-0">&rsaquo;</span>
              <span>Support weekly Python and web-development sessions for <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium">30+ learners</span>; help deliver project-based curriculum and debugging assistance</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            <span class="tech-badge">Python</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Web Dev</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Teaching</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-line mt-16 mb-16"></div>

    <!-- Education -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">Education</h2>

      <div class="relative pl-8 border-l border-surface-200">
        <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1 w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 ring-4 ring-surface-0"></div>
        <div class="glow-card p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-1">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Honours BSc in Computer Science</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500">2023 &mdash; Apr 2027</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium">Lakehead University &middot; Thunder Bay, ON</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm mt-3">Specialization in AI &amp; Web Development. <span class="text-zinc-200 font-medium">GPA: 3.7/4.0</span></p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-accent-500/10 text-accent-400 text-xs font-medium">Dean's List</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 text-xs font-medium">Tamblyn Merit Scholarship</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-3">Coursework: Data Structures &amp; Algorithms, OOP, Database Management, Machine Learning, Linear Algebra, Statistics</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
